%YAML 1.1
%TAG !u! tag:unity3d.com,2011:
--- !u!114 &11400000
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: e9620f8c34305754d8cc9a7e49e852d9, type: 3}
  m_Name: Ring Description_en
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  m_LocaleId:
    m_Code: en
  m_SharedData: {fileID: 11400000, guid: bb9e3674a6d3ebe459006565bb76908b, type: 2}
  m_Metadata:
    m_Items:
    - rid: 5901558492828794900
  m_TableData:
  - m_Id: 34152374272
    m_Localized: 'You feel powerful. Gives you {Power} strength. '
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
      - rid: 5901558492828794900
  - m_Id: 303578090115072
    m_Localized: Hurt who dare touches you! After someone melee attacks you, deal
      them {Power} Sharp Grass damage.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
      - rid: 5901558492828794900
  - m_Id: 304238512640000
    m_Localized: It's just hot. Grant you skill "Fireball".
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2499787767967744
    m_Localized: A ring inscribed with knowledge from all disciplines. Grant you
      skill "Omni Lecture".
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2499795581956096
    m_Localized: There is toxin circulating in your body. After you deal Bio damage,
      apply {Power} poison to your target.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
      - rid: 5901558492828794900
  - m_Id: 6584876163842048
    m_Localized: 'You feel healthy. Gives you {Power} max health. '
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
      - rid: 5901558492828794900
  - m_Id: 6585035681611776
    m_Localized: "From one comes two. After death, generate two weaker versions of
      yourself\u2014one inherits your left-hand rings, the other your right-hand
      rings. Your stats are split evenly between them."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 13543129278754816
    m_Localized: You feel hungry......
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 13560337082003456
    m_Localized: 'You feel hasty. Gives you {Power} speed. '
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
      - rid: 5901558492828794900
  - m_Id: 14975008838168576
    m_Localized: It summons a sword into your hand, embodying balance.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 16311391087407104
    m_Localized: Fortune smiles upon the untried. Every empty ring slot grants you
      {Power} critical hit and evasion.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
      - rid: 5901558492828794900
  - m_Id: 16324970045943808
    m_Localized: It summons a dagger into your hand, embodying deadliness.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 16333934615769088
    m_Localized: Your gaze becomes clear. Gain {Power} Accuracy.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
      - rid: 5901558492828794900
  - m_Id: 16334937016676352
    m_Localized: Your steps grow lighter. Gain {Power} Evasion.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
      - rid: 5901558492828794900
  - m_Id: 16335291418587136
    m_Localized: Your hand grows steadier. Gain {Power} Critical Hit.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
      - rid: 5901558492828794900
  - m_Id: 16335323093970944
    m_Localized: Your guard hardens. Gain {Power} Block.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
      - rid: 5901558492828794900
  - m_Id: 16338478468870144
    m_Localized: The wager grows riskier. At the end of battle, money gained or lost
      is increased by {Power}%.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
      - rid: 5901558492828794900
  - m_Id: 16373856353562624
    m_Localized: It summons an armor upon your body. Reduces {Power} Blunt damage,
      and reduces double that amount against Sharp damage.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
      - rid: 5901558492828794900
  - m_Id: 16374985858658304
    m_Localized: It summons a shield in your hand. When you block, reduce damage
      again by {Power}.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
      - rid: 5901558492828794900
  - m_Id: 17519281047515136
    m_Localized: It summons a gun into your hand. Modern in form, yet no stronger
      than any other ring's gift.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 17519276920320000
    m_Localized: It summons a bow into your hands. Distance is the promise of hunters'
      safety.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 17536989403197440
    m_Localized: Whoever stands in the front gets hit first. When there is any other
      frontline ally, the direct damage you take is {Power} % less effective.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
      - rid: 5901558492828794900
  - m_Id: 17536988161683456
    m_Localized: The closer you get, the more accurate. Gain +{Power} ACC on your
      melee actions.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
      - rid: 5901558492828794900
  - m_Id: 19198036524003328
    m_Localized: You've learned how to force enemies to reveal flaws in their frantic
      escape.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 19226502078263296
    m_Localized: Tooth is the hardest substance in human body. Why not use it to
      fight?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 19290622710378496
    m_Localized: A sudden urge compels you to mock your foes.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 22974090926559232
    m_Localized: Summons a staff into your hand. Actions scaling with Mind are {Power}%
      more effective. Can also be used to bash enemies.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
      - rid: 5901558492828794900
  - m_Id: 23710886634496000
    m_Localized: 'Summons a pickaxe into your hand. Great for mining ores, or breaking
      armors. '
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 23941880600481792
    m_Localized: 'Apply to the most previously equipped action: After each use, that
      action''s power increases by {Power}%.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
      - rid: 5901558492828794900
  - m_Id: 24234634882732032
    m_Localized: 'It teaches you the best angle to toss sand. '
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25026040027041792
    m_Localized: Water can flow or it can crash. Be water, my friend. (But now it
      doesn't hurt)
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25097594870059008
    m_Localized: "Nature has many ways to protect itself, and poison is one of them.
      \nAfter you deal Grass damage, apply {Power} stack of Poisoned to the same
      target. "
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
      - rid: 5901558492828794900
  - m_Id: 25117574302945280
    m_Localized: 'The first lesson in Grass magic class. '
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25328676919988224
    m_Localized: Your fire lasts longer but burns weaker. {Power}% of your Fire damage
      is converted into Burning at a 10:1 ratio.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
      - rid: 5901558492828794900
  - m_Id: 25512110409797632
    m_Localized: 'Mind is what you need for magic and prayer. Gives you {Power} mind. '
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
      - rid: 5901558492828794900
  - m_Id: 25693223161843712
    m_Localized: "Shrink the previously equipped weapon that is so its recovery time
      \xD70.5 and power -{Power}."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
      - rid: 5901558492828794900
  - m_Id: 25693225007337472
    m_Localized: "Enlarge the previously equipped weapon that is so its recovery
      time \xD71.5 and power +{Power}."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
      - rid: 5901558492828794900
  - m_Id: 25760312971120640
    m_Localized: This is what you get for not wearing gloves.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25824549512826880
    m_Localized: 'Wrathfire is also fire. Set fire to wrathfire. '
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 26053582657835008
    m_Localized: Enchant your previously equipped weapon, causing it to deal Fire
      Thermal damage equal to {Power}% of its original damage.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
      - rid: 5901558492828794900
  - m_Id: 26213872947056640
    m_Localized: You spread so much fire that it becomes a wall. This is level 2
      Fire skill and it must be equipped after a level 1 Fire skill.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 26230484639043584
    m_Localized: You feel energetic. Gain {Power} max mana.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
      - rid: 5901558492828794900
  - m_Id: 26487472681799680
    m_Localized: 'Continuously channel mana into fire, shaping it into a ray. Level
      2 Fire skill requires to equip level 1 Fire skill first. '
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 29337278152179712
    m_Localized: "Forged in sacrifice, it grants the bearer fire unending\u2014but
      only by feeding on their own flesh."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 29455745446576128
    m_Localized: The ultimate secret art among fire magic and prayers.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 29460834060075008
    m_Localized: The most dangerous mage is the one about to complete their chant.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 40586208737988608
    m_Localized: With enough knowledge and power, men can even create stars.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 40586562057768960
    m_Localized: People realize your heat without even touching you.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 40586556022165504
    m_Localized: Fire builds your body. Gain 100% resistance to Fire, 50% resistance
      to Grass, and 50% weakness to Water and Ice.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 40586525084979200
    m_Localized: Commonly equipped by summons, this ring enables its owner to make
      independent move decisions.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 41247830989049856
    m_Localized: Redirect all effects caused by you to the target you targeted last.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 41247824110391296
    m_Localized: Before dying, explode and deal {Power}% of your Max HP Fire Thermal
      damage to your last targeted character.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
      - rid: 5901558492828794900
  - m_Id: 41341278198927360
    m_Localized: Necessary in all circumstances.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 43818806851375104
    m_Localized: As long as you ask nicely, Mr. Sky will surely grant such a small
      request!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 43818800341815296
    m_Localized: Reminds one of something sad...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 43818808394878976
    m_Localized: The high density and imcompressibility of water makes it fit the
      job.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 43818809267294208
    m_Localized: You wish you have a surfboard.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 43818809900634112
    m_Localized: It costs less energy to draw from nearby resources than to create
      them from the void.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 43818810542362624
    m_Localized: They gasp for air, but only water answers.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 43909738137358336
    m_Localized: Be sure to treasure your food!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 43916694755446784
    m_Localized: "It doesn\u2019t take effect right away, but it\u2019s all-natural
      and free of additives."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 44172978697338880
    m_Localized: A plant that drains nutrients from the blood, burdens the nervous
      system, and dulls the mind.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 44511699271483392
    m_Localized: An exquisite creation born for artists.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 45067439119859712
    m_Localized: The mother tree of many cultures in the Natural World.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 45067440562700288
    m_Localized: People in the Natural World use it as a sharp scarecrow.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 45071622925516800
    m_Localized: You feel in a good mood. Raise MP Regen by {Power}.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
      - rid: 5901558492828794900
  - m_Id: 45071622216679424
    m_Localized: You feel your pain easing. Raise HP Regen by {Power}.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
      - rid: 5901558492828794900
  - m_Id: 45074607231533056
    m_Localized: If you have the Form of Element Ring, your Bio damage will convert
      to the element type of the previously equipped ring.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 45088260542496768
    m_Localized: Beauty is proven useful even on the battlefield.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 51071107598266368
    m_Localized: 'Harmony arises only when each plays their part.

      When all
      allies equip this protocol: your highest stat +{Power}, all stats -{Power2}.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 54531239946166272
    m_Localized: Sustain life by desire. Actions targeting allies gain {Power}.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
      - rid: 5901558492828794900
  - m_Id: 54531238402662400
    m_Localized: Govern the world by reason. Actions targeting no creature gain {Power}.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
      - rid: 5901558492828794900
  - m_Id: 54531239207968768
    m_Localized: Defend order by spirit. Actions targeting enemies gain {Power}.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
      - rid: 5901558492828794900
  - m_Id: 55792916192763904
    m_Localized: 'No matter how matter shifts, only form defines the self.

      After
      making melee contact with an ally, both units'' HP are averaged.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 55805083814141952
    m_Localized: All is Apeiron. Both the damage you deal and the damage you receive
      have no element.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  references:
    version: 2
    RefIds:
    - rid: 5901558492828794900
      type: {class: SmartFormatTag, ns: UnityEngine.Localization.Metadata, asm: Unity.Localization}
      data:
        m_Entries: 
